        <li><strong>Usage Information</strong>: pages visited, features used, and actions taken.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies and Similar Technologies</strong>: to enhance the user experience. Users may manage cookie preferences through their browser settings.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
